		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="422" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">魔花果实发射碎片袭击玩家，每个碎片造成<span color="#99ffff">50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="447" width="438" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">击碎魔花果实后，会反噬并暂时瘫痪<span textDecoration="underline">魔花</span><span>，同时掉落5个</span><span textDecoration="underline">魔花精粹</span><span>；一段时间后魔花会吸收魔花精粹并恢复。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1411" y="671" width="420" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#fcace5">(缩小前)<span color="#ffffff">魔花不断产生雪球下坠，每个造成</span><span color="#99ffff">50%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="895" width="421" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#acf8f8">(缩小后)<span color="#ffffff">魔花钻入地面，再在玩家处快速钻出，造成</span><span color="#99ffff">100%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1411" y="1119" width="435" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#acf8f8">(缩小后)<span color="#ffffff">魔花朝玩家扔出3个雪球，每个造成</span><span color="#99ffff">60%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#2686a2" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#2686a2">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="408" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" textDecoration ="underline" color="#ffffff">魔花果实<span textDecoration="none">对玩家进行连续的下落攻击，每次造成</span><span textDecoration="none" color="#99ffff">100%</span><span textDecoration="none">伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="447" width="418" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">魔花果实召唤1-2个<span color="#bfffff">大型冰史莱姆</span><span>，无伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="671" width="438" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">魔花旋转其花叶，造成<span color="#99ffff">100%</span><span>伤害，不论大小状态均会施放。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="895" width="434" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#fcace5">(缩小前)<span color="#ffffff">魔花使用花冠不断放出3排的雪球滚落，接触造成</span><span color="#99ffff">100%,50%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1119" width="434" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#acf8f8">(缩小后)<span color="#ffffff">魔花朝玩家连续发射总计9个的冰弹，每个造成</span><span color="#99ffff">20%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
