		<RichText x="66" y="1100" width="439" height="97" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">魔花：<span color="#99ffff">100冻</span><span>盾，击破使其永久缩小。<br/>魔花果实：7次(下落/召唤型)2次(攻击型)次数盾，击破后魔花-</span><span color="#99ffff">32冻</span><span>。<br/>魔花精粹：拾取前台角色-1.5%HP/s，可叠加独立计算。被魔花吸收后，每颗恢复魔花</span><span color="#99ffff">10冻</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
